[asy]

pair WW,X,Y,Z;

Z = (0,0);

Y = (12,0);

WW = (12,18);

X= (18,18);

draw(WW--X--Y--Z--WW);

label("$W$",WW,N);

label("$X$",X,N);

label("$Y$",Y,S);

label("$Z$",Z,S);

[/asy]

Output final answer with the format <<<answer>>> such as <<<123.42>>>, <<<125.0>>>, <<<-9867>>>.
